---
layout: default
stylesheets:
    - article
---
<section class='hero hero--page'>
    <div class='u-wrapper'>
        <p class='hero__eyebrow'>The case for JMAP</p>
        <h1 class='hero__h1'>Why JMAP?</h1>
        <p class='hero__sub'>
            IMAP turns 40 this year. The case for replacing it — grounded in benchmarks, implementation experience, and
            the realities of modern email infrastructure.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class='section section--document'>
    <div class='u-wrapper u-article-split'>
        <nav class='u-toc-wrapper'>{% include toc.liquid html=content class='u-toc' h_min=2 h_max=2 %}</nav>
        <article class='u-article'>{{ content }}</article>
    </div>
</section>

<button
    class='toc-fab'
    id='toc-fab'
    aria-label='Table of contents'
    aria-expanded='false'
    aria-controls='toc-drawer'
    hidden
>
    {% include icons/hamburger.liquid %}
</button>

<div
    class='toc-drawer'
    id='toc-drawer'
    role='dialog'
    aria-label='Table of contents'
    aria-modal='true'
    hidden
>
    <div class='toc-drawer__backdrop' data-toc-close></div>
    <div class='toc-drawer__panel'>
        <div class='toc-drawer__header'>
            <span class='toc-drawer__title'>Contents</span>
            <button class='toc-drawer__close' data-toc-close aria-label='Close'>
                {% include icons/close.liquid %}
            </button>
        </div>
        <nav class='toc-drawer__nav' id='toc-drawer-nav'></nav>
    </div>
</div>
